, "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1773031925.934391", "card_id": "Q_2013243480667808034", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 140}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "人大代表建议 「中小学春秋假也要考虑家长放假」，这一建议可行性如何？如何才能真正让家长「安心陪伴」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，全国人大代表张健建议：中小学在推行春秋假的同时，应当考虑家长的休假时间。他认为，只有将带薪休假制度与中小学春秋假有机结合，才能从根本上解决「孩子放假无人看管」的难题，实现孩子开心、家长安心。目前，政府工作报告也明确提出，支持有条件的地方推广中小学春秋假，落实职工带薪错峰休假制度。「中小学春秋假，也要考虑家长放假」，这条建议感动家长，冲上热搜 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f996788ddf76448277c9310572c428fb.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2013243480667808034"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIweSL8ue7n8R0EAMaCTExODY1NDIxNCD6yanNBjAAOMcBQBNyEzIwMTMyNDM0ODA2Njc4MDgwMzR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1773031925.934805", "card_id": "Q_1984302824536895750", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 23}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2026 年极简人的不购买清单是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "回看 2025 年的购物记录，有哪些物品会组成你明年的不购买清单？原因是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c46bb57b72fff9c50b2465fcfbc8766a_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1984302824536895750"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIweSL8ue7n8R0EAMaCTExNzczNDMxNCDjt4TKBjAAOEhAFHITMTk4NDMwMjgyNDUzNjg5NTc1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1773031925.935103", "card_id": "Q_448037876", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 83}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么野球场上的人很少打挡拆，就是你给他当左边他非要跑右边？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8b8c4773678e4f4e09a4dac128eb2d25_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"},